      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, what about the perspective that these benefits actually help people get back into the workforce long-term? like by providing stability so they can afford training or childcare? it seems like some experts argue the safety net actually supports the economy by stabilizing consumption. why aren't you bringing up those arguments?",
